    person("Ronald G. Thomas", email = "rgthomas@ucsd.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for reproducible research collaboration using Docker containers. 
    Provides R interfaces to create, manage, and collaborate on research projects with standardized 
    Docker environments, automated CI/CD workflows, and team collaboration tools.
